There are some new features added with CSS 3:

1. In below transition and the img:hover are new properties that came up with CSS 3

img {
	width: 450px;
	height: 500px;
	margin: 10px;
	transition: all 1s;
}


img:hover {
	transform: scale(1.1);
}


...there are others like animation etc.,


===============

reponsive UI:

It means your website is supporting all the devices and resolutions. No matter what devices we use website should
be responsive.. Responsive should be a priority while building websites.


